{"version":1,"entries":{"person_6005158_translations":{"at":1773688719079,"data":{"id":6005158,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"Gisele Lima é atriz brasileira nascida em São Paulo. Formada pelo curso de teatro Fátima do Vale e graduada em Rádio, TV e Internet, construiu sua trajetória artística atuando em diversas campanhas publicitárias e produções audiovisuais.\n\nIntegrou o núcleo principal da série “Até Onde Ele Vai”, da Univer Vídeo, e participou da série “Sintonia”, da Netflix, além de outros projetos independentes.\n\nAtualmente, além do trabalho como atriz, também atua na área de dublagem, ampliando sua presença e versatilidade no mercado audiovisual.","name":"","primary":false}}]}},"tv_81081_credits":{"at":1773688720846,"data":{"cast":[],"crew":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1047602,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Shigeo Koshi","original_name":"腰繁男","popularity":0.4618,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"5c6822f80e0a267b909cba1f","department":"Directing","job":"Director"},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":76409,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Noboru Ishiguro","original_name":"石黒昇","popularity":0.6923,"profile_path":"/3XF7rUIDxjWJhjTiCHgspPOC90I.jpg","credit_id":"5c6823040e0a267b909cba44","department":"Directing","job":"Director"},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":2243464,"known_for_department":"Sound","name":"Nobuyuki Koshibe","original_name":"Nobuyuki Koshibe","popularity":0.0286,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"5c6823340e0a266daca07206","department":"Sound","job":"Music"},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":2243465,"known_for_department":"Art","name":"Shuichi Ishibashi","original_name":"Shuichi Ishibashi","popularity":0.0338,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"5c6823560e0a267de6a105b6","department":"Art","job":"Art Direction"}],"id":81081}},"person_148891_translations":{"at":1773688721231,"data":{"id":148891,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Lee Heung-Kam","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"在澳门长大的李香琴一直迷恋粤剧，尤以任剑辉为甚，并决心以舞台艺术为其终身职业。早年在广州学艺，并随戏班下乡，来港后继续其花旦行档，擅演反派，堪称“西宫王”（又称“奸妃琴”）。60年代末开始电视生涯，她主持的《群星会》有极多的拥趸。1972年起在无线和亚视间走来走去，但不论在哪个台，她在时装剧、古装剧都有极精彩的表现，并经常作粤剧演出。1998年离开亚视后，没有再在电视台亮相，但仍有在外地登台。","name":"李香琴","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"李香琴，原名李瑞琴，人稱「琴姐」，祖籍廣東順德勒流鎮番村，香港女演員，前無綫電視及亞洲電視女藝員，投身電影及電視劇界前於粵劇出身。\n\n李香琴因於電影《鴛鴦江遺恨》飾演反派而成名，之後長時間在電影中演出反派，因而成為粵語片年代少有的反派女角代表，有「一代奸妃」和「西宮琴」之稱。直到 1970 年代起加入電視圈，才主要改為出演正派角色。她的誼父是影星張活遊。","name":"李香琴","primary":true}}]}},"tv_254166_keywords":{"at":1773688722100,"data":{"id":254166,"results":[{"name":"law firm","id":162813},{"name":"workplace comedy","id":210605}]}},"person_2797422_translations":{"at":1773688724391,"data":{"id":2797422,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"2001年9月14日出生于河北省石家庄市，中国内地男演员。 2019年4月，参加腾讯视频青年团训节目《创造营2019》，从而进入演艺圈；9月，主演青春甜宠励志剧《甜了青梅配竹马》；同年10月，参加青春体娱跨界类型节目《超新星全运会第二季》。2020年4月，出演的校园爱情剧《致我们甜甜的小美满》播出；8月，主演青春校园剧《我和我的时光少年》，饰演施澈一角。","name":"任世豪","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ren Shihao","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"任世豪","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Nhậm Thế Hào","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"2001 年 9 月 14 日出生於河北省石家莊市，中國內地男演員。\n\n2019 年 4 月，參加騰訊視頻青年團訓節目《創造營 2019》，從而進入演藝圈；9 月，主演青春甜寵勵志劇《甜了青梅配竹馬》；同年 10 月，參加青春體娛跨界類型節目《超新星全運會第二季》。2020 年 4 月，出演的校園愛情劇《致我們甜甜的小美滿》播出；8 月，主演青春校園劇《我和我的時光少年》，飾演施澈一角。","name":"任世豪","primary":false}}]}},"person_1820716_translations":{"at":1773688729024,"data":{"id":1820716,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Pam Kearns","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Памела Смит","primary":false}}]}},"person_224414_translations":{"at":1773688729461,"data":{"id":224414,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Wakana Matsumoto is a Japanese actress from Tottori Prefecture. She portrayed Airi Nogami in the tokusatsu drama Kamen Rider Den-O.","name":"Wakana Matsumoto","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"松本若菜","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"松本若菜（Wakana Matsumoto），1984年2月25日出生于日本鸟取县，模特、演员，隶属于“”トリプルエー“事务所。","name":"松本若菜","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"松本若菜","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Wakana Macumoto","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Вакана Мацумото","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"松本若菜","primary":false}}]}},"person_1259680_translations":{"at":1773688729890,"data":{"id":1259680,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"萨哈拉·桑卡布理查，1968年5月4日生于泰国曼谷，歌手、吉他手、演员、模特。\n\n泰国家喻户晓的影视歌三栖巨星，是泰国第一支长盛不衰的经典乐队NUVO乐队的主唱兼吉他手，发行过多张专辑，拥有众多泰国人民耳熟能详的经典歌曲。并成功的主演过多部电影和电视剧。他在泰国的歌迷和影迷年龄跨度很大，因其德艺双馨，才华横溢，是影迷心中的梦幻男主角和歌迷心中的偶像英雄。其主演的电视剧《俏女佣》《满天繁星》《天使之争》和《花环夫人》也曾在中国播出。","name":"萨哈拉·桑卡布理查","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"สหรัถ สังคปรีชา","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Saharat Sangkapreecha","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"薩哈拉·桑卡布理查，1968 年 5 月 4 日生於泰國曼谷，歌手、吉他手、演員、模特。\n\n泰國家喻戶曉的影視歌三棲巨星，是泰國第一支長盛不衰的經典樂隊 NUVO 樂隊的主唱兼吉他手，發行過多張專輯，擁有眾多泰國人民耳熟能詳的經典歌曲。併成功的主演過多部電影和電視劇。他在泰國的歌迷和影迷年齡跨度很大，因其德藝雙馨，才華橫溢，是影迷心中的夢幻男主角和歌迷心中的偶像英雄。其主演的電視劇《俏女傭》《滿天繁星》《天使之爭》和《花環夫人》也曾在中國播出。","name":"薩哈拉·桑卡布理查","primary":false}}]}},"person_232808_translations":{"at":1773688729962,"data":{"id":232808,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Qiao Zhenyu","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"乔振宇，演员，毕业于北京舞蹈学院。因出演《浣花洗剑录》中方宝玉一角而走红，成为当红小生。亦被大陆网民选为第一届天涯四美之一。","name":"乔振宇","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"喬振宇","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Цяо Чжэнь Юй","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kiều Chấn Vũ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"교진우","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"喬振宇，演員，畢業於北京舞蹈學院。因出演《浣花洗劍錄》中方寶玉一角而走紅，成為當紅小生。亦被大陸網民選為第一屆天涯四美之一。","name":"喬振宇","primary":fa